{"tid":1283452,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"外國人支持香港人反送中 全世界都知道發生咩事","createTime":"2019-07-03T20:45:21.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-04T03:37:57.000Z","uid":110564,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"b304e42a2ee19a9ed9a74e4d759d31c81cf61e00","tid":1283452,"uid":110564,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T20:45:21.000Z","msg":"知道大家過去一個月好辛苦<br />\n如果你地仲係覺得絕望嘅睇下世界上有幾多人關心我地<br />\n啱啱YouTube睇到條片想share比大家<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/08xPR755MPI\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F08xPR755MPI&d=U4JEvS4lHdpitRbH3ga0O0cGFqE5jXx4AE4DM0839cs%3D&h=fba2689a\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/08xPR755MPI</a><br />\n<br />\n唔好再話好辛苦 要交比其他人<br />\n唔好再話自己己經做晒可以做嘅野 <br />\n我地的確未爭取到任何嘢 但係成效已經開始見到 <br />\n全世界都留意到我哋 為民主自由嘅付出<br />\n<br />\n當你覺得心灰意冷嘅時候 諗下過去一個月一齊發夢嘅兄弟<br />\n當你感到徬徨無助嗰時 諗下世界各地對我地嘅支持<br />\n<br />\n唔好再做其他毫無實際嘅事 繼續去做返應該要做嘅野<br />\n<br />\nwe stop being ourselves, when we stop standing up for the things that matter<br />\n<br />\n香港加油"},{"pid":"01f7642c06684a14dfb0c44c7ed779e289cca37b","tid":1283452,"uid":110564,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T20:47:00.000Z","msg":"如果可以 會唔會有人整合到報紙以外嘅外地支援資訊"},{"pid":"69535f14db87fb9cf4339ce2942b6696f73acb58","tid":1283452,"uid":110564,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T20:47:41.000Z","msg":"隔離post都有越南人寫畀我哋嘅歌"},{"pid":"fbad5af76c7351fe51a5203a227e45f4c37e59ca","tid":1283452,"uid":239205,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T03:34:26.000Z","msg":"其實有思考能力既都唔會支持呢條例 撐得既多數都係冇腦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e9c89819193331788a7b5f85737d52251aac1fe0","tid":1283452,"uid":25108,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T03:37:57.000Z","msg":"全世界都知有咩用<br />\n中國：中國內政<br />\n777:一切照舊"}]}